###  https://w3id.org/pmd/automatce/AUTOMATCE_0030005
<https://w3id.org/pmd/automatce/AUTOMATCE_0030005> rdf:type owl:Class ;
                                                   rdfs:subClassOf <https://w3id.org/pmd/automatce/AUTOMATCE_0030003> ;
